# Skill Routing

Before implementing, map task type to skills:

- Library/API/framework questions or code examples -> use Context7 MCP first.
- Plugin architecture/discoverability/manifest decisions -> use `plugin-architect`.
- Rule authoring requests (`/create-rule`, `.cursor/rules/`) -> use `create-rule`.
- Supply-chain policy changes -> follow `rules/core-runtime.mdc` and deterministic checks.

If a required skill is available, load/follow it before editing files.
